Option  = get input from user
    if option is manual, ask user to enter words comma separated
    if option if file, ask user for the full path, including file name
        if file not recognised show warning and ask if want to continue
            if yes - go to 1st step
            if no - exit app
    if option not recognised show warning and ask if want to continue
        if yes - go to 1st step
        if no - exit app

    load the list of words specified by the user for unscrambling the scrambled words
    start matching scrambled words against the loaded word list
        for each scrambled word in specified scrambled words
            for each unscrambled word in word list
                if scrambled word == unscrambled word , add to the list of matched
                otherwise
                    sort scrambled word
                    sort unscrambled word
                    if sorted scrambled word == sorted unscrambled word , add to the list of matched

        if match is found, show matched scrambled word for all unscrambled words
        otherwise, show message that no matches were found

ask if user wants to continue
